[
  {
    "text": "Voss peels back the skin along the forearm with a scalpel.",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "The blade is surgical steel.",
    "start": 2.92,
    "end": 3.98
  },
  {
    "text": "The tissue beneath should be fascia and muscle.",
    "start": 4.5,
    "end": 6.22
  },
  {
    "text": "It is not.",
    "start": 7.14,
    "end": 7.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Beneath the skin runs a lattice of something crystalline,",
    "start": 8.58,
    "end": 11.14
  },
  {
    "text": "threaded through the muscle fibers like roots through soil.",
    "start": 11.44,
    "end": 13.8
  },
  {
    "text": "The crystal pulses,",
    "start": 14.64,
    "end": 15.36
  },
  {
    "text": "faintly,",
    "start": 16.22,
    "end": 16.74
  },
  {
    "text": "slowly,",
    "start": 17.54,
    "end": 18.06
  },
  {
    "text": "in rhythm with the Neanderthals heart.",
    "start": 18.76,
    "end": 20.32
  },
  {
    "text": "He has seen this before, non-biology textbooks, in electronics manuals.",
    "start": 21.32,
    "end": 26.2
  },
  {
    "text": "The crystal is a conductor.",
    "start": 27.04,
    "end": 28.36
  },
  {
    "text": "The room pattern is a circuit.",
    "start": 28.92,
    "end": 30.42
  },
  {
    "text": "The Neanderthals body is not just flesh, it is a living weapon system,",
    "start": 31.68,
    "end": 35.74
  },
  {
    "text": "engineered across generations,",
    "start": 36.26,
    "end": 37.44
  },
  {
    "text": "grown into the bone and blood of a species that was supposed to be extinct for 40,000 years.",
    "start": 38.26,
    "end": 42.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Voss sets down the scalpel.",
    "start": 43.86,
    "end": 45.12
  },
  {
    "text": "His hands are steady.",
    "start": 45.98,
    "end": 46.7
  },
  {
    "text": "His pulse is not.",
    "start": 47.6,
    "end": 48.44
  },
  {
    "text": "He writes one word in his notebook, frequency.",
    "start": 49.92,
    "end": 53.28
  },
  {
    "text": "If the rooms are circuits, they resonate at a frequency.",
    "start": 54.2,
    "end": 57.08
  },
  {
    "text": "If you can find that frequency, he can disrupt the circuit.",
    "start": 57.8,
    "end": 60.48
  },
  {
    "text": "If he can disrupt the circuit, the bone armor is just boon.",
    "start": 61.1,
    "end": 64.02
  },
  {
    "text": "The soldier guard shifts his weight.",
    "start": 64.8,
    "end": 66.08
  },
  {
    "text": "The captured Neanderthals eyes open.",
    "start": 66.78,
    "end": 68.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Amber.",
    "start": 69.38,
    "end": 69.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Ancient.",
    "start": 70.68,
    "end": 70.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Aware.",
    "start": 71.8,
    "end": 72.12
  },
  {
    "text": "It looks at Voss and its lips move around the breathing tube.",
    "start": 72.9,
    "end": 75.98
  },
  {
    "text": "The sound is wet and low.",
    "start": 76.68,
    "end": 78.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Not a word.",
    "start": 79.38,
    "end": 80.06
  },
  {
    "text": "A vibration.",
    "start": 80.86,
    "end": 81.46
  },
  {
    "text": "The monitor's spike.",
    "start": 82.44,
    "end": 83.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Then flatline.",
    "start": 83.94,
    "end": 84.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Then recover.",
    "start": 85.38,
    "end": 86.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Voss watches the data.",
    "start": 87.08,
    "end": 88.02
  },
  {
    "text": "His lips press together.",
    "start": 88.7,
    "end": 89.66
  },
  {
    "text": "He has 40 out hours before the next assault.",
    "start": 90.3,
    "end": 92.64
  },
  {
    "text": "He intends to use every minute.",
    "start": 93.38,
    "end": 94.88
  }
]